item.title: CVE-2023-0865|2023-03-20T15:52:15.223Z -- unknown -- woocommerce%20multiple%20customer%20addresses%20%26%20shipping
item.description: The WooCommerce Multiple Customer Addresses & Shipping WordPress plugin before 21.7 does not ensure that the address to add/update/retrieve/delete and duplicate belong to the user making the request, or is from a high privilege users, allowing any authenticated users, such as subscriber to add/update/duplicate/delete as well as retrieve addresses of other users.
